---
const colorIcons = "white";
import Elipsis from "./Elipsis.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="bg-black height:100vh py-10 mb mb-5">
        <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-16 lg:px-6">
            <div class="mb-15 leading-none tracking-tight text-white" style="text-align: left;">
                <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold">
                    <Elipsis />
                    Donde la creatividad encuentra la estrategia.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-2xl font-normal">
                    Más que una agencia, una extensión de tu equipo.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 md:space-y-0">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-12 lg:w-12 dark:bg-primary-900">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-{colorIcons}" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6.025A7.5 7.5 0 1 0 17.975 14H10V6.025Z"/>
                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.5 3c-.169 0-.334.014-.5.025V11h7.975c.011-.166.025-.331.025-.5A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 13.5 3Z"/>
                          </svg>                          
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">Branding Estratégico.</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
                        Nuestro equipo de expertos en branding te ayudará a crear una marca que se destaque en la competencia y que conecte con tus clientes de manera emocional.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-12 lg:w-12 dark:bg-primary-900">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-{colorIcons}" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 12c.263 0 .524-.06.767-.175a2 2 0 0 0 .65-.491c.186-.21.333-.46.433-.734.1-.274.15-.568.15-.864a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 .586 1.591c.375.422.884.659 1.414.659.53 0 1.04-.237 1.414-.659A2.4 2.4 0 0 0 12 9.736a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 .586 1.591c.375.422.884.659 1.414.659.53 0 1.04-.237 1.414-.659A2.4 2.4 0 0 0 16 9.736c0 .295.052.588.152.861s.248.521.434.73a2 2 0 0 0 .649.488 1.809 1.809 0 0 0 1.53 0 2.03 2.03 0 0 0 .65-.488c.185-.209.332-.457.433-.73.1-.273.152-.566.152-.861 0-.974-1.108-3.85-1.618-5.121A.983.983 0 0 0 17.466 4H6.456a.986.986 0 0 0-.93.645C5.045 5.962 4 8.905 4 9.736c.023.59.241 1.148.611 1.567.37.418.865.667 1.389.697Zm0 0c.328 0 .651-.091.94-.266A2.1 2.1 0 0 0 7.66 11h.681a2.1 2.1 0 0 0 .718.734c.29.175.613.266.942.266.328 0 .651-.091.94-.266.29-.174.537-.427.719-.734h.681a2.1 2.1 0 0 0 .719.734c.289.175.612.266.94.266.329 0 .652-.091.942-.266.29-.174.536-.427.718-.734h.681c.183.307.43.56.719.734.29.174.613.266.941.266a1.819 1.819 0 0 0 1.06-.351M6 12a1.766 1.766 0 0 1-1.163-.476M5 12v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2v-5h3v5h7a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-7m-5 3v2h2v-2h-2Z"/>
                          </svg>                          
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">Marketing Digital y Automatización.</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
                        Aumenta tus conversiones y reduce tus costos con nuestras estrategias de marketing digital y automatización.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-12 lg:w-12 dark:bg-primary-900">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-{colorIcons} lg:w-6 lg:h-6 dark:text-primary-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 6V5a3 3 0 013-3h2a3 3 0 013 3v1h2a2 2 0 012 2v3.57A22.952 22.952 0 0110 13a22.95 22.95 0 01-8-1.43V8a2 2 0 012-2h2zm2-1a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v1H8V5zm1 5a1 1 0 011-1h.01a1 1 0 110 2H10a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path><path d="M2 13.692V16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2.308A24.974 24.974 0 0110 15c-2.796 0-5.487-.46-8-1.308z"></path></svg>                    
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">Investigación de mercado y tendencias.</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
                        Ofrecemos un análisis exhaustivo del mercado y las tendencias emergentes para garantizar que tu negocio esté siempre un paso adelante.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-12 lg:w-12 dark:bg-primary-900">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-{colorIcons}" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.6 16.733c.234.269.548.456.895.534a1.4 1.4 0 0 0 1.75-.762c.172-.615-.446-1.287-1.242-1.481-.796-.194-1.41-.861-1.241-1.481a1.4 1.4 0 0 1 1.75-.762c.343.077.654.26.888.524m-1.358 4.017v.617m0-5.939v.725M4 15v4m3-6v6M6 8.5 10.5 5 14 7.5 18 4m0 0h-3.5M18 4v3m2 8a5 5 0 1 1-10 0 5 5 0 0 1 10 0Z"/>
                          </svg>                          
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">Posicionamiento.</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
                        Contamos con expertos en ventas y posicionamiento que te ayudarán a identificar oportunidades de crecimiento y a desarrollar estrategias efectivas para aumentar tus ventas.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
</section>
<section style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%;  mb-10">
    <div class="min-w-1/4" style=" display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 100%;">
        <button  class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center p-1 mb-2 me-2 overflow-hidden text-lg font-medium rounded-lg group bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-200 via-yellow-300 to-yellow-500 text-white hover:text-gray-900 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-yellow-400">
            <span class="font-bold relative px-8 py-3 transition-all ease-in duration-75 bg-black rounded-md group-hover:bg-transparent group-hover:dark:bg-transparent">
                Catálogo
            </span>
        </button>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    button span {
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        min-width: 200px; ;
        max-width: none; /* Elimina el max-width para pantallas grandes */
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        button span {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        button span {
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
    }
</style>